Phase 1–2: Setup & Requirement Gathering

Mostly documentation, no coding yet.

GitHub content:

docs/Requirements.md → Project requirements, objectives, use cases

docs/ERD.png → Entity Relationship Diagram of objects (Tender, Contract, Bid)

Phase 3–4: Object & Field Setup

Salesforce custom objects and fields.

GitHub content:

metadata/objects/ → Include object metadata XML (Tender__c.object, Contract__c.object)

metadata/fields/ → Custom fields’ XML if separate

Optional: Create a diagram showing object relationships for reference.

Phase 5: Validation Rules & Workflow

Salesforce business rules.

GitHub content:

metadata/validationRules/ → XML files for validation rules

metadata/workflows/ → Workflow metadata (field updates, email alerts)

Documentation: docs/Validation_Workflows.md explaining rules

Phase 6: Apex Classes & Triggers

Any custom logic you wrote in Apex.

GitHub content:

src/classes/ → .cls files for Apex classes
Example: TenderTriggerHandler.cls

src/triggers/ → .trigger files
Example: TenderTrigger.trigger

Documentation: docs/Apex_Logic.md explaining each trigger/class purpose

Phase 7–8: Data Management

Data import/export logic.

GitHub content:

data/ → Sample CSVs used for import

scripts/DataLoader_Instructions.md → Steps or script for loading data

metadata/duplicateRules/ → XML of duplicate rules

Phase 9: Reports, Dashboards & Security

Reports, dashboards, and security configurations.

GitHub content:

metadata/reports/ → Report metadata XML

metadata/dashboards/ → Dashboard XML

metadata/sharingSettings/ → Sharing rules XML

metadata/profiles/ → Field-level security XML

docs/Security_Configuration.md → Explain OWD, FLS, Login IP, Session Settings

Phase 10: Final Presentation & Demo

Presentation and handoff documents.

GitHub content:

docs/Pitch_Presentation.pptx or PDF

docs/Demo_Video.mp4 (optional)

docs/Project_Handoff.md → Include screenshots, instructions, metadata overview

docs/LinkedIn_Portfolio.md → Public showcase info

Suggested GitHub Folder Structure
/Salesforce-Tender-Project
│
├─ docs/
│   ├─ Requirements.md
│   ├─ ERD.png
│   ├─ Validation_Workflows.md
│   ├─ Apex_Logic.md
│   ├─ DataLoader_Instructions.md
│   ├─ Security_Configuration.md
│   ├─ Project_Handoff.md
│   ├─ LinkedIn_Portfolio.md
│   └─ Pitch_Presentation.pptx
│
├─ data/
│   └─ SampleData.csv
│
├─ metadata/
│   ├─ objects/
│   ├─ fields/
│   ├─ validationRules/
│   ├─ workflows/
│   ├─ reports/
│   ├─ dashboards/
│   ├─ sharingSettings/
│   ├─ profiles/
│   └─ duplicateRules/
│
├─ src/
│   ├─ classes/
│   │   └─ TenderTriggerHandler.cls
│   └─ triggers/
│       └─ TenderTrigger.trigger
